norn (0.12.1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * UPnP/NAT-PMP auto port mapping with SSDP discovery and SOAP
    AddPortMapping; tries NAT-PMP first, falls back to UPnP.
  * NAT traversal integrated into norn_listen_async() — mapped external
    endpoint is fed back to the DHT layer via net_set_mapped_endpoint().
  * nornd now uses a dedicated Ed25519 identity at ~/.config/norn/identity
    instead of ~/.ssh/id_ed25519; auto-generates on first start.
  * norn node public / norn node secret — IPC verbs to query nornd's
    in-memory keys over the Unix socket.
  * norn --help wraps at terminal width (TIOCGWINSZ / COLUMNS / 80).
  * norn_upnp.c added to the library build.

 -- norn maintainers <16991612+nostra124@users.noreply.github.com>  Mon, 29 Jun 2026 00:00:00 +0000

norn (0.12.0) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Package the norn stack: libnorn (shared library), libnorn-dev
    (headers/.pc/static lib), norn (norn/nornd/norn-forward + units), and
    libnorn-doc (Doxygen API reference + design docs).
  * Ships the v0.12.0 milestone: the nornd node daemon and the norn IPC CLI
    over the Raft-replicated cluster key-value store.

